Hey everyone,
    Well I'm still alive and at NMSU. This is my last semester though.  I should hopeful;ly be going to Arazona next year.  It is going to be hard moving even farther from my friends and leaving my friends here.  Expeacially now.  college is the best time of your life don't let anyone tell you diffrent but you must leave eventually. Unless your name is Patric and you are a 7th yr sr. Long story if you don't understand.  I have come by the school and talked to you guys some of you have grown up so much even for just less then a year.  When I go back I feel really old, but I'm always happy to see you guys.  Some of you are just like my family and I think about you all the time so stay safe and know that I love you.  I just wanted to write a lil note now that I'm done. Let me say once again I love you.

Ok so this is it.  I'm not goin to hide ANymore.  I'm not one to hide so I have no Idea why I have been doing it so much but now its time for it to stop.  Jon is gone yet again, he is sposted to leave to Iraq again In febuary, I'm so happy :( But I mean what can you do.  Ummmmm I was goin out with this other guy for a while wrong thing to do. Moved way to fast and now feel like he is stacker boy and have no one here to save me from him.  He calls all the time and tells my voice mail that he loves me but he scares me, hes not the nices guy when he has been drinking and hes got kids and well the list goes on and If you can't tell Its not like I'm ready to setle anyway. I mean there are still these feelings for Jon but I mean there will always be and with him coming in and out of my life like he does right now I can't just be with one person.  I think I do just fine as a free agant.  When I need to feel loved I mean I have friends shit I have a lot of them and I know they are there when I need them so Its not like i'm alone so why be tied down.  I was told college is the best times of your life and at frist I never thought It could top some of thoses High school Moments "SPRING BREAK" for example but man it has.  I never want it to end but it might and sooner then exspected to but we will just have to see.  It has its ups and downs but thats Life The people that you meet in colege and become close friends to will always be you friends.  They will see you at your worst and at your best.  But they will never leave.  But you need to be free so you can see all of this.  I never relized this until just the other day.  I know if I need the "boyfriend" figure I have him but when I'm there I need nothing but goodtimes and friends. Parties and memories that will last forever.  Its great and I hope you all have loved you time where you are as much as I Have. LOVE YOU ALL

PARTY ON

JEss
